The Connoisseur, a one of a kind, first of its type event in East and Central Africa took place on Saturday courtesy of Radio Africa Group. Sponsored by Safaricom, the wine and whisky festival at Delta Towers, was an experience in itself. Not only was the beverage list curated, so was the guest list.Oysters and Sauvignon Blanc, Glenlivet Founders special tasting, Afternoon tea with Martell, the Macallan tasting, Old Fashioned Hour with singleton sunray cocktails, Wine and Cheese board, Wine Culture with Baraka and the Jameson mixology masterclass were some of the experiences you missed out on.